Subject: [PATCH] video: fbdev: au1200fb: Return an error code if a memory allocation fails
Git-commit: 8cae353e6b01ac3f18097f631cdbceb5ff28c7f3
Patch-mainline: v4.15-rc1
References: bsc#1051510

'ret' is known to be 0 at this point.
In case of memory allocation error in 'framebuffer_alloc()', return
-ENOMEM instead.

